ActOlympic and Paralympic Marks Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule 2 to the Olympic and Paralympic Marks Act
PrecisOrder Amending Schedule 2 to the OLYMPIC AND PARALYMPIC MARKS ACT by adding 38 new marks (4 words and 34 graphic designs) and prohibiting them from being used by any person (including businesses) for business purposes until December 31, 2010, unless a specified exception in the Act applies.
